   <concept id="FAR_19_811_3"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.2"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.811-3</ph> Contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1219e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1253e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> The contracting officer shall
insert the clause at <xref href="52.219-11.dita#FAR_52_219_11"
                        base="i1057684"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-11</xref>,
Special 8(a) Contract Conditions, in contracts between the SBA and
the agency when the acquisition is accomplished using the procedures
of <xref href="19.811-1.dita#FAR_19_811_1"
                        base="i1100035"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.811-1</xref>(a) and (b).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1253e21" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> The contracting
officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.219-12.dita#FAR_52_219_12"
                        base="i1057700"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-12</xref>, Special 8(a)
Subcontract Conditions, in contracts between the SBA and its 8(a)
contractor when the acquisition is accomplished using the procedures
of <xref href="19.811-1.dita#FAR_19_811_1"
                        base="i1100035"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.811-1</xref>(a) and (b).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1253e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> The contracting
officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.219-17.dita#FAR_52_219_17"
                        base="i1057772"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-17</xref>, Section 8(a)
Award, in competitive solicitations and contracts when the acquisition
is accomplished using the procedures of <xref href="19.805.dita#FAR_19_805"
                        base="i1099961"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.805</xref> and in sole source
awards which utilize the alternative procedure in <xref href="19.811-1.dita#FAR_19_811_1"
                        base="i1100035"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.811-1</xref>(c).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1253e46" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph> The contracting
officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.219-18.dita#FAR_52_219_18"
                        base="i1057789"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-18</xref>, Notification
of Competition Limited to Eligible 8(a) Participants, in competitive
solicitations and contracts when the acquisition is accomplished
using the procedures of <xref href="19.805.dita#FAR_19_805"
                        base="i1099961"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.805</xref>. The
clause at <xref href="52.219-18.dita#FAR_52_219_18"
                        base="i1057789"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-18</xref> with its Alternate
I shall be used when competition is to be limited to 8(a) participants
within one or more specific SBA districts pursuant to <xref href="19.804-2.dita#FAR_19_804_2"
                        base="i1099900"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.804-2</xref>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1253e63" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph> For contracts
or orders resulting from this subpart, see <xref href="19.507.dita#FAR_19_507"
                        base="i1100931"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(e) for use of <xref href="52.219-14.dita#FAR_52_219_14"
                        base="i1057730"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-14</xref>, Limitations
on Subcontracting, and <xref href="19.507.dita#FAR_19_507"
                        base="i1100931"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(h)
for use of <xref href="52.219-33.dita#FAR_52_219_33"
                        base="id203KG0I04WS"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-33</xref>,
Nonmanufacturer Rule.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
